ne one, he nearly timed his form and his race to perfection to cause a major upset to Romania's David Popovici, the clear pre-race favourite.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7809266295014888, \"rank\": 0.16891285408549003, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Popovici\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Popovici\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Popovici\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Popovici\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lane\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"his form\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"his race\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"a major upset\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Popivici only managed to touch two hundredths ahead of Richards in a blanket finish, which saw Duncan Scott edged out into fourth.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Popivici\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"a blanket finish\", \"from\": 883