": 1302, \"to\": 1321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It seems that way,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I can not be too disappointed with that.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My first individual at an Olympic Games so to come away with a silver is great.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My first individual\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be two one hundredths off gold is excruciatingly frustrating.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two one hundredths\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought I had got it, it felt as if I had touched it first.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The time says differently.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The time\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not a sport that is up for debate, it is black and white.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"debate\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't my best finish, I would be lying if I said it was fantastic.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best finish\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We move on, we get better and try to get it next time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scott had warned he needed to swim the fastest 200m of his career but he came up just shor